---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | SESEC"
  description="SESEC's privacy policy. Information about how we collect, use and protect your personal data."
  lang="en"
>
  <Section title="Privacy Policy" padding="xl">
    <div class="legal-content">
      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>1. Data Controller</h3>
        <p>The data controller responsible for processing your personal data is:</p>
        
        <div class="company-info">
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Company:</strong> SESEC</li>
            <li><strong>Activity:</strong> Cybersecurity Consulting</li>
            <li><strong>Address:</strong> Spain</li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@sesecpro.com</li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +34 XXX XXX XXX</li>
            <li><strong>Website:</strong> www.sesecpro.com</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>2. Data We Collect</h3>
        
        <h4>2.1 Contact Information</h4>
        <p>When you contact us through our forms or email, we may collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name and surname</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Phone number</li>
          <li>Company name</li>
          <li>Message content</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>2.2 Technical Information</h4>
        <p>When you visit our website, we automatically collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>IP address</li>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Operating system</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
          <li>Referral source</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>3. Purpose of Processing</h3>
        <p>We process your personal data for the following purposes:</p>
        
        <h4>3.1 Service Provision</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and requests</li>
          <li>Provide cybersecurity consulting services</li>
          <li>Maintain customer relationships</li>
          <li>Process service contracts</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>3.2 Website Improvement</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Analyze website usage and performance</li>
          <li>Improve user experience</li>
          <li>Ensure website security</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>3.3 Legal Compliance</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
          <li>Maintain accounting records</li>
          <li>Handle legal claims</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>4. Legal Basis</h3>
        <p>The legal basis for processing your data depends on the purpose:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Consent:</strong> When you voluntarily provide information through forms</li>
          <li><strong>Contractual necessity:</strong> To fulfill service agreements</li>
          <li><strong>Legitimate interest:</strong> For website analytics and security</li>
          <li><strong>Legal obligation:</strong> To comply with applicable laws</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>5. Data Retention</h3>
        <p>We retain your personal data for the following periods:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact inquiries:</strong> 2 years from last contact</li>
          <li><strong>Service contracts:</strong> 6 years after contract termination</li>
          <li><strong>Website analytics:</strong> 26 months maximum</li>
          <li><strong>Legal obligations:</strong> As required by applicable law</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>6. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>Under the GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>
        
        <h4>6.1 Access and Portability</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Right to access your personal data</li>
          <li>Right to data portability</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>6.2 Correction and Deletion</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Right to rectify inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>6.3 Processing Limitations</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Right to restrict processing</li>
          <li>Right to object to processing</li>
          <li>Right to withdraw consent</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at: <a href="mailto:privacy@sesecpro.com">privacy@sesecpro.com</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>7. Data Security</h3>
        <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Encryption of data in transit and at rest</li>
          <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
          <li>Regular security assessments</li>
          <li>Staff training on data protection</li>
          <li>Incident response procedures</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>8. Data Sharing</h3>
        <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share data with:</p>
        
        <h4>8.1 Service Providers</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Cloud hosting providers</li>
          <li>Email service providers</li>
          <li>Analytics services</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>8.2 Legal Requirements</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Law enforcement agencies (when legally required)</li>
          <li>Regulatory authorities</li>
          <li>Courts and legal proceedings</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>9. International Transfers</h3>
        <p>If we transfer your data outside the EU, we ensure adequate protection through:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Adequacy decisions by the European Commission</li>
          <li>Standard Contractual Clauses</li>
          <li>Binding Corporate Rules</li>
          <li>Certification schemes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>10. Cookies</h3>
        <p>Our website uses cookies as described in our <a href="/en/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a>. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>11. Updates</h3>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>12. Supervisory Authority</h3>
        <p>You have the right to lodge a complaint with the Spanish Data Protection Agency (AEPD) if you believe your rights have been violated:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Website:</strong> www.aepd.es</li>
          <li><strong>Address:</strong> C/ Jorge Juan, 6, 28001 Madrid, Spain</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h3>13. Contact</h3>
        <p>For any questions about this privacy policy or data protection:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@sesecpro.com">privacy@sesecpro.com</a></li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +34 XXX XXX XXX</li>
          <li><strong>Address:</strong> Spain</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2025</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .legal-section h3 {
    color: var(--fg);
    font-size: var(--fs-h3);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .legal-section h4 {
    color: var(--fg);
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-2) 0;
  }
  
  .legal-section p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  
  .legal-section ul {
    margin: var(--space-3) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--dur) var(--ease);
  }
  
  .legal-section a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-2);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  /* Company Info Styles */
  .company-info {
    background: var(--glass);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    margin: var(--space-4) 0;
  }
  
  .company-info ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }
  
  .company-info li {
    padding: var(--space-2) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  
  .company-info li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  
  .company-info strong {
    color: var(--fg);
    display: inline-block;
    min-width: 140px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-content {
      padding: 0 var(--space-4);
    }
    
    .legal-section h3 {
      font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    }
    
    .company-info {
      padding: var(--space-4);
    }
    
    .company-info strong {
      min-width: auto;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
    }
  }
</style>